name: Villa Gede Batulumbang
address: FXHV+X38, Antap, Selemadeg, Tabanan Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: We had an amazing week at this Airbnb home! Everything was absolutely delightful! The house exceeded all our expectations. Everything was new and spotlessly clean, and the space was just stunning. The pool was clean, well-maintained, and deep, which was a real treat. Having a separate kitchen was incredibly convenient. Breakfasts prepared for us each morning were a lovely surprise. We also arranged for a masseuse to come to the villa, and it was an incredible relaxation experience. We would happily return here again and again! Thank you so much for the wonderful hospitality!
review 2: For an authentic Bali experience, look no further then Villa Gede! The staff were very friendly and welcoming! Breakfast was made on the spot every day, and we even had a couple of spa treatments on the property to make our stay even more enjoyable.
review 3:
Wonderful place amazing a bit of paradise.

The perfect place if you want to chill and relax without all the stress of the city neighbour

You're a bit far from city center but it definitely deserve it.
review 5: Wonderful place where to spend your family holidays. Flowering garden with clean rooms, cool pool, friendly staff...

name: Warung Triple B - Bebek Bumbu Bali
address: FXGR+QGW, Antap, Selemadeg, Tabanan Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: Lovely Warung serving duck on the main road between Soka and Balian. I had the grilled duck which was tasty and succulent, my husband had the fried duck which he also really enjoyed. Served with rice and Sambal matah which was also good. Great price.  There are other options if you don't want duck. Chicken was also very good. Pineapple juice was lovely and cold.  The warung is clean,has a small view of the ocean and a nice breeze blows through. Friendly staff.  There is parking so take time to stop on this busy road.
review 2: This is a great place for duck. We had the grilled duck and the Bebek Betutu. Both were delicious. This place hasn't been open long but hopefully does very well. Lovely atmosphere with a view of gardens and the ocean.
